&lt;p&gt;The first time I learned the figure‑eight, it was 6 a.m., coffee in a paint-stained thermos, and a living room taped up like a crime scene. The house belonged to a neighbor who’d done an earnest DIY skim coat. The seams were proud, ridges crisp as a credit card. I’d already spent too many nights fighting walls with the wrong motion: straight up and down, back and forth, carving tracks with a pole head that liked to dig in at the end of each stroke. If you’ve ever wrestled a pole sander drywall on a long seam, you know that end-of-stroke gouge—the one that laughs at you when the primer hits it.&lt;/p&gt;</summary><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/images/brand/12.webp" medium="image"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/07/figure-eight-motion-for-pole-sander-on-walls-pole-sander-drywall/cards/facebook/figure-eight-motion-for-pole-sander-on-walls-pole-sander-drywall.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/07/figure-eight-motion-for-pole-sander-on-walls-pole-sander-drywall/cards/facebook/figure-eight-motion-for-pole-sander-on-walls-pole-sander-drywall.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/07/figure-eight-motion-for-pole-sander-on-walls-pole-sander-drywall/cards/facebook/figure-eight-motion-for-pole-sander-on-walls-pole-sander-drywall.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/07/figure-eight-motion-for-pole-sander-on-walls-pole-sander-drywall/cards/instagram/figure-eight-motion-for-pole-sander-on-walls-pole-sander-drywall.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/07/figure-eight-motion-for-pole-sander-on-walls-pole-sander-drywall/cards/instagram/figure-eight-motion-for-pole-sander-on-walls-pole-sander-drywall.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/07/figure-eight-motion-for-pole-sander-on-walls-pole-sander-drywall/cards/instagram/figure-eight-motion-for-pole-sander-on-walls-pole-sander-drywall.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/07/figure-eight-motion-for-pole-sander-on-walls-pole-sander-drywall/cards/pinterest/figure-eight-motion-for-pole-sander-on-walls-pole-sander-drywall.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/07/figure-eight-motion-for-pole-sander-on-walls-pole-sander-drywall/cards/pinterest/figure-eight-motion-for-pole-sander-on-walls-pole-sander-drywall.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/07/figure-eight-motion-for-pole-sander-on-walls-pole-sander-drywall/cards/pinterest/figure-eight-motion-for-pole-sander-on-walls-pole-sander-drywall.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/07/figure-eight-motion-for-pole-sander-on-walls-pole-sander-drywall/cards/facebook/figure-eight-motion-for-pole-sander-on-walls-pole-sander-drywall.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/07/figure-eight-motion-for-pole-sander-on-walls-pole-sander-drywall/cards/facebook/figure-eight-motion-for-pole-sander-on-walls-pole-sander-drywall.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/07/figure-eight-motion-for-pole-sander-on-walls-pole-sander-drywall/cards/facebook/figure-eight-motion-for-pole-sander-on-walls-pole-sander-drywall.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><readingTime>11</readingTime></item><item><title>Set Up Dustless Drywall Sanding With Shop Vac</title><link>https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/21/set-up-dustless-drywall-sanding-with-shop-vac-dustless-drywall-sanding/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/21/set-up-dustless-drywall-sanding-with-shop-vac-dustless-drywall-sanding/</guid><pubDate>Fri, 21 Nov 2025 16:22:15 +0000</pubDate><category>Drywall Sanding</category><category>grit-120</category><category>grit-220</category><category>dust control</category><description>Learn how to set up dustless drywall sanding with a shop vac for cleaner, faster results. Pro-tested gear, step-by-step setup, and practical sanding tips.</description><summary>&lt;h2 id="dustless-drywall-sanding-with-a-shop-vac-setup"&gt;Dustless drywall sanding with a shop vac setup&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I’ve walked into more living rooms covered in drywall dust than I care to admit. It’s in the couch seams, the AC returns, your morning coffee—everywhere. You think you’ll “just scuff the patches,” then the sun hits the air like a stage light and there it is: a snow globe from floor to ceiling. I’ve been there—rushed deadlines, fresh paint booked for tomorrow, and a client who can’t breathe if dust drifts beyond the plastic. That’s why I preach dust control like it’s a religion, especially when we’re sanding drywall. With a proper setup for dustless drywall sanding using a shop vac, you don’t just keep the room livable—you work faster, see your surface better, and stop clogging your lungs and your vacuum.&lt;/p&gt;</summary><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/images/brand/27.webp" medium="image"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/21/set-up-dustless-drywall-sanding-with-shop-vac-dustless-drywall-sanding/cards/facebook/set-up-dustless-drywall-sanding-with-shop-vac-dustless-drywall-sanding.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/21/set-up-dustless-drywall-sanding-with-shop-vac-dustless-drywall-sanding/cards/facebook/set-up-dustless-drywall-sanding-with-shop-vac-dustless-drywall-sanding.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/21/set-up-dustless-drywall-sanding-with-shop-vac-dustless-drywall-sanding/cards/facebook/set-up-dustless-drywall-sanding-with-shop-vac-dustless-drywall-sanding.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/21/set-up-dustless-drywall-sanding-with-shop-vac-dustless-drywall-sanding/cards/instagram/set-up-dustless-drywall-sanding-with-shop-vac-dustless-drywall-sanding.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/21/set-up-dustless-drywall-sanding-with-shop-vac-dustless-drywall-sanding/cards/instagram/set-up-dustless-drywall-sanding-with-shop-vac-dustless-drywall-sanding.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/21/set-up-dustless-drywall-sanding-with-shop-vac-dustless-drywall-sanding/cards/instagram/set-up-dustless-drywall-sanding-with-shop-vac-dustless-drywall-sanding.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/21/set-up-dustless-drywall-sanding-with-shop-vac-dustless-drywall-sanding/cards/pinterest/set-up-dustless-drywall-sanding-with-shop-vac-dustless-drywall-sanding.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/21/set-up-dustless-drywall-sanding-with-shop-vac-dustless-drywall-sanding/cards/pinterest/set-up-dustless-drywall-sanding-with-shop-vac-dustless-drywall-sanding.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/21/set-up-dustless-drywall-sanding-with-shop-vac-dustless-drywall-sanding/cards/pinterest/set-up-dustless-drywall-sanding-with-shop-vac-dustless-drywall-sanding.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/21/set-up-dustless-drywall-sanding-with-shop-vac-dustless-drywall-sanding/cards/facebook/set-up-dustless-drywall-sanding-with-shop-vac-dustless-drywall-sanding.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/21/set-up-dustless-drywall-sanding-with-shop-vac-dustless-drywall-sanding/cards/facebook/set-up-dustless-drywall-sanding-with-shop-vac-dustless-drywall-sanding.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/21/set-up-dustless-drywall-sanding-with-shop-vac-dustless-drywall-sanding/cards/facebook/set-up-dustless-drywall-sanding-with-shop-vac-dustless-drywall-sanding.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><readingTime>13</readingTime></item><item><title>Level 4 Versus Level 5 Wall Finish Explained</title><link>https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/10/level-4-versus-level-5-wall-finish-explained-wall-finishing/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/10/level-4-versus-level-5-wall-finish-explained-wall-finishing/</guid><pubDate>Mon, 10 Nov 2025 21:32:57 +0000</pubDate><category>Drywall Sanding</category><category>grit-150</category><category>grit-180</category><category>grit-220</category><category>grit-240</category><category>grit-320</category><category>grit-800</category><category>joint compound</category><category>clear coat</category><description>Engineer’s guide to Level 4 vs Level 5 drywall: optics, materials, costs, tests, and tips to choose the right wall finishing for paint and lighting.</description><summary>&lt;h2 id="level-4-vs-level-5-wall-finishing-explained"&gt;Level 4 vs Level 5 Wall Finishing Explained&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Even before the paint dries, the room tells you what you need to know. You step into a newly built living room at dusk. The pendant over the kitchen island throws a narrow cone; the western window sends a low, grazing wash across the longest wall. With the light switch up, the seams show themselves—not as obvious ridges, but as faint bands where reflectance changes with every step. The drywallers did everything “by the book.” Joints are filled, feathered, and sanded. Primer looks even. But the optics betray the truth: the wall absorbs and reflects differently where paper meets compound. That’s the moment when wall finishing becomes the difference between “good” and “finished.”&lt;/p&gt;</summary><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/10/level-4-versus-level-5-wall-finish-explained-wall-finishing/cards/facebook/level-4-versus-level-5-wall-finish-explained-wall-finishing.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/10/level-4-versus-level-5-wall-finish-explained-wall-finishing/cards/facebook/level-4-versus-level-5-wall-finish-explained-wall-finishing.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/10/level-4-versus-level-5-wall-finish-explained-wall-finishing/cards/facebook/level-4-versus-level-5-wall-finish-explained-wall-finishing.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/10/level-4-versus-level-5-wall-finish-explained-wall-finishing/cards/instagram/level-4-versus-level-5-wall-finish-explained-wall-finishing.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/10/level-4-versus-level-5-wall-finish-explained-wall-finishing/cards/instagram/level-4-versus-level-5-wall-finish-explained-wall-finishing.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/10/level-4-versus-level-5-wall-finish-explained-wall-finishing/cards/instagram/level-4-versus-level-5-wall-finish-explained-wall-finishing.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/10/level-4-versus-level-5-wall-finish-explained-wall-finishing/cards/pinterest/level-4-versus-level-5-wall-finish-explained-wall-finishing.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/10/level-4-versus-level-5-wall-finish-explained-wall-finishing/cards/pinterest/level-4-versus-level-5-wall-finish-explained-wall-finishing.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/10/level-4-versus-level-5-wall-finish-explained-wall-finishing/cards/pinterest/level-4-versus-level-5-wall-finish-explained-wall-finishing.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/10/level-4-versus-level-5-wall-finish-explained-wall-finishing/cards/facebook/level-4-versus-level-5-wall-finish-explained-wall-finishing.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/10/level-4-versus-level-5-wall-finish-explained-wall-finishing/cards/facebook/level-4-versus-level-5-wall-finish-explained-wall-finishing.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/10/level-4-versus-level-5-wall-finish-explained-wall-finishing/cards/facebook/level-4-versus-level-5-wall-finish-explained-wall-finishing.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><readingTime>11</readingTime></item><item><title>How Long To Wait Before Sanding Joint Compound</title><link>https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/04/how-long-to-wait-before-sanding-joint-compound-joint-compound-sanding/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/04/how-long-to-wait-before-sanding-joint-compound-joint-compound-sanding/</guid><pubDate>Tue, 04 Nov 2025 17:23:25 +0000</pubDate><category>Drywall Sanding</category><category>grit-150</category><category>grit-180</category><category>grit-220</category><category>grit-320</category><category>joint compound</category><category>dust control</category><description>Learn precise wait times, drying variables, and pro sanding workflows to prevent gouges and dust when sanding joint compound.</description><summary>&lt;h2 id="how-long-to-wait-for-joint-compound-sanding"&gt;How Long to Wait for Joint Compound Sanding&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It’s 10:47 p.m. You’ve spent the evening in a quiet room, spreading thin, even passes of mud across seams that once shadowed your drywall. The lights are low; the blade marks are almost gone. You resist the urge to sand right now because experience whispers that impatience leads to rework. The air smells faintly of gypsum and paint primer, and the walls look nearly finished—but the clock matters more than appearances. Joint compound sanding isn’t just a step; it’s the inflection point between a surface that telegraphs flaws under paint and one that disappears behind a flawless finish.&lt;/p&gt;</summary><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/04/how-long-to-wait-before-sanding-joint-compound-joint-compound-sanding/cards/facebook/how-long-to-wait-before-sanding-joint-compound-joint-compound-sanding.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/04/how-long-to-wait-before-sanding-joint-compound-joint-compound-sanding/cards/facebook/how-long-to-wait-before-sanding-joint-compound-joint-compound-sanding.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/04/how-long-to-wait-before-sanding-joint-compound-joint-compound-sanding/cards/facebook/how-long-to-wait-before-sanding-joint-compound-joint-compound-sanding.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/04/how-long-to-wait-before-sanding-joint-compound-joint-compound-sanding/cards/instagram/how-long-to-wait-before-sanding-joint-compound-joint-compound-sanding.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/04/how-long-to-wait-before-sanding-joint-compound-joint-compound-sanding/cards/instagram/how-long-to-wait-before-sanding-joint-compound-joint-compound-sanding.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/04/how-long-to-wait-before-sanding-joint-compound-joint-compound-sanding/cards/instagram/how-long-to-wait-before-sanding-joint-compound-joint-compound-sanding.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/04/how-long-to-wait-before-sanding-joint-compound-joint-compound-sanding/cards/pinterest/how-long-to-wait-before-sanding-joint-compound-joint-compound-sanding.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/04/how-long-to-wait-before-sanding-joint-compound-joint-compound-sanding/cards/pinterest/how-long-to-wait-before-sanding-joint-compound-joint-compound-sanding.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/04/how-long-to-wait-before-sanding-joint-compound-joint-compound-sanding/cards/pinterest/how-long-to-wait-before-sanding-joint-compound-joint-compound-sanding.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/04/how-long-to-wait-before-sanding-joint-compound-joint-compound-sanding/cards/facebook/how-long-to-wait-before-sanding-joint-compound-joint-compound-sanding.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/04/how-long-to-wait-before-sanding-joint-compound-joint-compound-sanding/cards/facebook/how-long-to-wait-before-sanding-joint-compound-joint-compound-sanding.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/04/how-long-to-wait-before-sanding-joint-compound-joint-compound-sanding/cards/facebook/how-long-to-wait-before-sanding-joint-compound-joint-compound-sanding.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><readingTime>10</readingTime></item><item><title>Best Grit For Drywall Sanding Before Paint</title><link>https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/02/best-grit-for-drywall-sanding-before-paint-drywall-sanding/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/02/best-grit-for-drywall-sanding-before-paint-drywall-sanding/</guid><pubDate>Sun, 02 Nov 2025 20:40:05 +0000</pubDate><category>Drywall Sanding</category><category>grit-120</category><category>grit-180</category><category>grit-220</category><category>wet sanding</category><category>dust control</category><category>joint compound</category><category>sanding block</category><description>Discover expert tips and best practices for drywall sanding to achieve a perfect paint-ready surface. Learn about grit selection and techniques.</description><summary>&lt;h2 id="mastering-drywall-sanding-for-a-flawless-finish"&gt;Mastering Drywall Sanding for a Flawless Finish&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;There’s something incredibly satisfying about transforming a raw, uneven drywall surface into a smooth, pristine canvas ready for a fresh coat of paint. Picture this: you’ve just finished a long day at work, but instead of collapsing on the couch, you step into your garage, grab your sanding tools, and lose yourself in the rhythmic motion of perfecting your drywall. The hum of the sander drowns out the day’s stress, and as each layer of dust falls, so too does the weight of your worries.&lt;/p&gt;</summary><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/02/best-grit-for-drywall-sanding-before-paint-drywall-sanding/cards/facebook/best-grit-for-drywall-sanding-before-paint-drywall-sanding.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/02/best-grit-for-drywall-sanding-before-paint-drywall-sanding/cards/facebook/best-grit-for-drywall-sanding-before-paint-drywall-sanding.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/02/best-grit-for-drywall-sanding-before-paint-drywall-sanding/cards/facebook/best-grit-for-drywall-sanding-before-paint-drywall-sanding.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/02/best-grit-for-drywall-sanding-before-paint-drywall-sanding/cards/instagram/best-grit-for-drywall-sanding-before-paint-drywall-sanding.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/02/best-grit-for-drywall-sanding-before-paint-drywall-sanding/cards/instagram/best-grit-for-drywall-sanding-before-paint-drywall-sanding.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/02/best-grit-for-drywall-sanding-before-paint-drywall-sanding/cards/instagram/best-grit-for-drywall-sanding-before-paint-drywall-sanding.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/02/best-grit-for-drywall-sanding-before-paint-drywall-sanding/cards/pinterest/best-grit-for-drywall-sanding-before-paint-drywall-sanding.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/02/best-grit-for-drywall-sanding-before-paint-drywall-sanding/cards/pinterest/best-grit-for-drywall-sanding-before-paint-drywall-sanding.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/02/best-grit-for-drywall-sanding-before-paint-drywall-sanding/cards/pinterest/best-grit-for-drywall-sanding-before-paint-drywall-sanding.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/02/best-grit-for-drywall-sanding-before-paint-drywall-sanding/cards/facebook/best-grit-for-drywall-sanding-before-paint-drywall-sanding.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/02/best-grit-for-drywall-sanding-before-paint-drywall-sanding/cards/facebook/best-grit-for-drywall-sanding-before-paint-drywall-sanding.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/02/best-grit-for-drywall-sanding-before-paint-drywall-sanding/cards/facebook/best-grit-for-drywall-sanding-before-paint-drywall-sanding.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><readingTime>6</readingTime></item></channel></rss>